  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In the first year the project did not support any certification costs but supported the cassava analysis for the Mole region. In the second project year, support for initial certification was offered in the four project countries as follows: in Ghana the Damango cassava group was supported to achieve first certification; the same happened in Burkina with the Neboun and Toudou group; in Togo the project supported the Solaris initiative with the cost of first certification of the pineapple farmer groups around Nots&#xE9;; in Sao Tom&#xE9; OM4D financed the certification costs of Bela Vista.</narrative>
